data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
This step will check for new Sets release since the last DB update. If new Sets are found, all the card records from those sets are going to be update (This include brand new MasterCards and new SetCards from already existing MasterCards).
At the end of this step we should have a up to date MasterCard list.
Appr. Execution time: 45 Mins. Per 100 new Mastercards.

data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
This OPTIONAL step will retry the manual searches in Prodeck for Mastercards still missing their Prodeck URL/Passcodes. Try this again just to check if Prodeck has "Fix" some of their records. This will also try to find the TCG Player URLs/Prices for any Setcard still missing theirs.
At the end of this step we should have less cards with missing data.
Appr. Execution time: TBD

data.name: label7.Text
data.value:
This step doesn't require an automation script to run in the background. For any new Mastercard added to the DB whose Passcode has been update (this is done via Prodeck by obtaining its URL) We can obtain their card image by going into this URL: [https://images.ygoprodeck.com/images/cards/<passcode>.jpg"]
Copy all the auto-generated URLs below, paste them into JDownloader and drownload the images into \Images\Cards of this app. Click "Refresh File" to verify files have been picked up correctly.

data.name: label12.Text
data.value:
This step will loop through all the Setcards with a TCG Player registered. This will update all the prices for each Setcard.
WARNING: By FEB 2024 there are ~34,000 SetCards in the DB... This means that the execution time to update the prices of the entire DB takes appr. 36 Hrs. Only run "Update Full DB" if you can leave your PC alone for that amount of time. Otherwise, simply update the prices of each set individually. (Whatever Sets are relevant to you)

data.name: label9.Text
data.value:
Last Notes before you go.
-Running Step 1 is all your need to have an up to date DB and start marking your cards.
-Running Step 2 will not guarantee that missing Prodeck/TCG Player URL will be found. For that reason, some records WILL need to be updated manually. Use the Override menus on the right side to do this.
-Step 3 Tab will ONLY generate the Card Images Download URLs for Mastercards whose Passcodes have been updated (this is done in automation when finding their prodeck URLs or overriding manually)
-You can find a Mastercard's Passcode anywhere online, you can override these even if there is not an available Prodeck URL.
-It is possible to mark missing URLs as "Unavailable" this is done to remove them from the "Missing URLs" list and keep them in the background as "URLs we just know they dont exists".
-Other then that, go manage your collection!
